The Telegraph - Calcutta : Bengal
 Sunday, July 18, 2004 				 Kuntal case 
																								Howrah, July 17: The mother and brother of an accused in the murder of Kuntal Sain today gave confessional statements, expressing their desire to turn approvers. 																								Police rejected the offer of Manjusha and Jyotirmoy, saying they have solved the case after the accused  Sampad Mukherjee, Manjushas son, and Arijit Pal  confessed. 																								Police believe it is a kidnap-for-cash attempt gone wrong. 
